            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">2</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Draw for first move:</span> Each player draws one tile — closest to A goes first. Replace tiles and draw your opening rack of seven.</p>
          </div>
