            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">3</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Play the game:</span> 25 minutes per player on chess clock. Record scores each turn. Play until one player uses all tiles or both players pass.</p>
          </div>
