      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Clock Rules & Time Penalties</h2>

      <p>Tournament Scrabble uses chess clocks — typically 25 minutes per player per game. Running out of time costs 10 points per minute exceeded, and going 10 minutes over means automatic forfeiture.</p>

